losophy\">The Philosophy</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"collapsed collection-link\" aria-controls=\"collapseExample\" aria-expanded=\"false\" role=\"button\" href=\"#collapseinnerlinks\" data-toggle=\"collapse\">The Collection </a>\n<div id=\"collapseinnerlinks\" class=\"collapse\">\n<ul class=\"collapseinnerlinks-ul\">\n<li><a href=\"https://loveindus.com/pages/amrutini\">Amrutini</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://loveindus.com/pages/velvet\">Velvet :08</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://loveindus.com/pages/freedom-of-expression\">Freedom of Expression</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ph-discover\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-3 offset-md-1\">\n<div class=\"ph-discover-inner\">\n<p class=\"ph-p ph-p-web\">Discover Love, Indus. Our product code and what sets us apart.</p>\n<p class=\"ph-p ph-p-ipad\">Discover Love, Indus.<br> Our product code and what sets us apart.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<div class=\"ph-discover-inner-right\">\n<h1 class=\"ph-h2\">The process of creation is tied to the 6 Ps of our product philosophy.</h1>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- <a class=\"btnJump\">Awards</a> -->\n<div class=\"ovr-hid pos-relative\">\n<div class=\"the_philosophy-slider-links\">\n<div class=\"link-circle\"><picture> <source srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/circle-web.png?v=1604683866\" media=\"(min-width:1351px)\"> <source srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/circle-ipad.png?v=1604683864\" media=\"(min-width:768px)\"> <img class=\"img-fluid img-responsive lazyload\" alt=\"Hexagone clircle\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/circle-mobile.png?v=1604683864\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/circle-mobile.png?v=1604683864\"> </picture></div>\n<div class=\"teal-triangle-links\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-12 text-center\">\n<div data-hashlink=\"#PreciousExtracts\" class=\"tringle-links\"><a class=\"btnJumpslider1 active\">Precious Extracts</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-6\">\n<div data-hashlink=\"#PurposefulDecisions\" class=\"tringle-links\"><a class=\"btnJumpslider6\">Purposeful Decisions</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-6\">\n<div data-hashlink=\"#ProvenPotency\" class=\"tringle-links\"><a class=\"btnJumpslider2\">Proven Potency</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-6\">\n<div data-hashlink=\"#PertinentProducts\" class=\"tringle-links\"><a class=\"btnJumpslider5\">Pertinent Products</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-6\">\n<div data-hashlink=\"#PrecisionInCreation\" class=\"tringle-links\"><a class=\"btnJumpslider3\">Precision in Creation</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-12 text-center\">\n<div data-hashlink=\"#PractitionersThatKnowTheirCraft\" class=\"tringle-links\"><a class=\"btnJumpslider4\">Practitioners that know their craft</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"myCarousel\" class=\"owl-carousel owl-theme the_philosophy-slider\">\n<div data-hash=\"PreciousExtracts\" class=\"item clearfix\">\n<div class=\"ph-slider-1\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-4 philosophy_div\"></div>\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<div class=\"the_philosophy-slider-content\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<p class=\"slider-number\">01</p>\n<div class=\"slider-line-top\"><img class=\"lazyload img-responsive img-fluid\" alt=\"Top Line\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\"></div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<div class=\"the_philosophy-slider-content-inner\">\n<p class=\"slider-untitle\">Where the Brew begins</p>\n<h2 class=\"slider-title\">Precious Extracts</h2>\n<p>We believe in the quality of our ingredients – the core of our products. The Indian sub-continent offers a smorgasbord of energy, rich soils, complex customs and heritage to choose from. From the mustard blooms of Punjab to the blazing orange <em>Palash</em> (Flame of the Forest) flowers of Maharashtra, we have thoughtfully curated and incorporated incredible minerals and ingredients - some lost, some forgotten and several that were undiscovered outside their regional bastions.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"slider-line-bottom\"><img class=\"lazyload img-responsive img-fluid\" alt=\"Bottom Line\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"slider-right-img\"><picture> <source srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider1_ddd786f8-ec9b-437e-9c6c-4faffc9a330b.png?v=1604684002\" media=\"(min-width:992px)\"> <source srcset=\"slider1-ipad_2782064e-2561-423f-9808-98e3d8b68829.png\" media=\"(min-width:768px)\"> <img class=\"img-fluid img-responsive lazyload\" alt=\"Precious Extracts\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider1-mobile_994a72cd-25e1-4717-bdbc-68d554169756.png?v=1604684002\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider1-mobile_994a72cd-25e1-4717-bdbc-68d554169756.png?v=1604684002\"> </picture></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-hash=\"ProvenPotency\" class=\"item clearfix\">\n<div class=\"ph-slider-2\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-4 philosophy_div\"></div>\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<div class=\"the_philosophy-slider-content the_philosophy-slider2-content\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<p class=\"slider-number\">02</p>\n<div class=\"slider-line-top\"><img class=\"lazyload img-responsive img-fluid\" alt=\"Top Line\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\"></div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<div class=\"the_philosophy-slider-content-inner\">\n<p class=\"slider-untitle\">Power packed products</p>\n<h2 class=\"slider-title\">Proven Potency</h2>\n<p>We believe in <span class=\"f-600\">maximal impact</span>. Our formulas pack 40+ ingredients into each bottle - because a single ingredient, no matter how powerful, cannot provide the multitude of benefits that a deliberately crafted concoction of super-ingredients can. The power of our extracts is further enhanced by new-age processes such as biotransformation and several other proprietary technologies to give you an exceptional skincare experience.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"slider-line-bottom\"><img class=\"lazyload img-responsive img-fluid\" alt=\"Bottom Line\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"slider-right-img\"><picture> <source srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider2_8243889f-9b3d-4f5f-852b-3cb9ce066078.png?v=1604684060\" media=\"(min-width:992px)\"> <source srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider2-ipad_a6ad3f85-03ec-48c9-90f6-d528457babff.png?v=1604684081\" media=\"(min-width:768px)\"> <img class=\"img-fluid img-responsive lazyload\" alt=\"Proven Potency\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider2-mobile_7e68f27b-6280-45bb-aa52-1a33d52e792a.png?v=1604684105\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider2-mobile_7e68f27b-6280-45bb-aa52-1a33d52e792a.png?v=1604684105\"> </picture></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-hash=\"PrecisionInCreation\" class=\"item clearfix\">\n<div class=\"ph-slider-3\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-4 philosophy_div\"></div>\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<div class=\"the_philosophy-slider-content the_philosophy-slider2-content\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<p class=\"slider-number\">03</p>\n<div class=\"slider-line-top\"><img class=\"lazyload img-responsive img-fluid\" alt=\"Top Line\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\"></div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<div class=\"the_philosophy-slider-content-inner\">\n<p class=\"slider-untitle\">Harmony in complexity</p>\n<h2 class=\"slider-title\">Precision in Creation</h2>\n<p>We believe that patience is a prerequisite for perfection. It has been a journey of over a hundred versions and iterations of our various formulas, distilling the essence of these incredible ingredients to find that delicate balance - between old and new, time-tested rituals and contemporary innovations - allowing each to complement and accentuate the other. It took almost five years before we were satisfied with what we have to offer you.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"slider-line-bottom\"><img class=\"lazyload img-responsive img-fluid\" alt=\"Bottom Line\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"slider-right-img\"><picture> <source srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider3_58e7039b-8f5f-4cc2-aa8d-f9c0bb407ba1.png?v=1604684131\" media=\"(min-width:992px)\"> <source srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider3-ipad_31c9deef-2f9f-44b3-ac40-bee047d8dd29.png?v=1604684131\" media=\"(min-width:768px)\"> <img class=\"img-fluid img-responsive lazyload\" alt=\"Precision in Creation\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider3-mobile_ab1d89c1-abd0-42a0-adcf-16b394f752c8.png?v=1604684160\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider3-mobile_ab1d89c1-abd0-42a0-adcf-16b394f752c8.png?v=1604684160\"> </picture></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-hash=\"PractitionersThatKnowTheirCraft\" class=\"item clearfix\">\n<div class=\"ph-slider-4\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-4 philosophy_div\"></div>\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<div class=\"the_philosophy-slider-content the_philosophy-slider4-content\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<p class=\"slider-number\">04</p>\n<div class=\"slider-line-top\"><img class=\"lazyload img-responsive img-fluid\" alt=\"Top Line\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\"></div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<div class=\"the_philosophy-slider-content-inner\">\n<p class=\"slider-untitle\">The creators and experts</p>\n<h2 class=\"slider-title\">Practitioners that know their Craft</h2>\n<p>We believe that exceptional creations require exceptional creators. So, we gathered a team of brilliant specialists in Eastern medicine and Western science to develop powerful solutions that combine the best of both worlds. From PhDs and patent-holders to holistic and indigenous beauty practitioners, from renowned chemists to Ayurveda doctors – many have helped inform and engineer these offerings.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"slider-line-bottom\"><img class=\"lazyload img-responsive img-fluid\" alt=\"Bottom Line\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"slider-right-img\"><img class=\"img-fluid img-responsive lazyload\" alt=\"Practitioners that know their Craft\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider4-mobile_e1cc1b70-b350-43b6-9b7d-408cc82771be.png?v=1604684196\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider4-mobile_e1cc1b70-b350-43b6-9b7d-408cc82771be.png?v=1604684196\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-hash=\"PertinentProducts\" class=\"item clearfix\">\n<div class=\"ph-slider-5\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-4 philosophy_div\"></div>\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<div class=\"the_philosophy-slider-content the_philosophy-slider5-content\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<p class=\"slider-number\">05</p>\n<div class=\"slider-line-top\"><img class=\"lazyload img-responsive img-fluid\" alt=\"Bottom Line\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\"></div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<div class=\"the_philosophy-slider-content-inner\">\n<p class=\"slider-untitle\">Transformative benefits</p>\n<h2 class=\"slider-title\">Pertinent Products</h2>\n<p>We believe in focusing on solutions that matter. Through research, in-depth analysis, social listening and other tools, we discovered, for example, that anti-aging is a limiting way to think of skin care. Hence the focus on building skin strength. Or that there are limited options for smokers’ lines, so we set out to create alternatives that would be relevant and beneficial for you.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"slider-line-bottom\"><img class=\"lazyload img-responsive img-fluid\" alt=\"Bottom Line\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-hash=\"PurposefulDecisions\" class=\"item clearfix\">\n<div class=\"ph-slider-6\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-4 philosophy_div\"></div>\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<div class=\"the_philosophy-slider-content the_philosophy-slider6-content\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<p class=\"slider-number\">06</p>\n<div class=\"slider-line-top\"><img class=\"lazyload img-responsive img-fluid\" alt=\"Top Line\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\"></div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n<div class=\"the_philosophy-slider-content-inner\">\n<p class=\"slider-untitle\">In every drop, every design-element, and every decision.</p>\n<h2 class=\"slider-title\">Purposeful Decisions</h2>\n<p class=\"mb-0\">We believe</p>\n<ul class=\"slider6-points\">\n<li><span>Toxins have no place in your beauty and wellness regimen.</span></li>\n<li><span>Artificial fragrances aren’t necessary.</span> In our products, the faint yet beautiful scent that lingers briefly on application has no synthetic components. Instead, it is a product of love and an artful blend of fragrant botanicals.</li>\n<li><span>Artificial colors are not meant for your skin</span> and that’s why there aren’t any camouflaging the contents in our jars. Any slight variations among units, or shifts in color over time, are driven by the natural beauty of the creation.</li>\n<li><span>Safety and well-being are top priorities.</span> All our products have gone through a rigorous protocol of safety, allergy and dermatologist testing.</li>\n<li><span>We must all do our bit for the planet.</span> We prefer to package in glass, and FSC certified paper containing up-cycled materials.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"slider6-last-line\">These are small, but deliberate steps – towards a bigger purpose.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"slider-line-bottom\"><img class=\"lazyload img-responsive img-fluid\" alt=\"Bottom Line\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider-line-top.png?v=1604683913\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"slider-right-img\"><picture> <source srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider6.png?v=1604684352\" media=\"(min-width:768px)\"> <img class=\"img-fluid img-responsive lazyload\" alt=\"Purposeful Decisions\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider6-mobile.png?v=1604684367\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/slider6-mobile.png?v=1604684367\"> </picture></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>",
